UML:TaggedValue.value: The fleet manager can compare fuel consumption between different drivers.
Depending on configuration, the in-vehicle transport management system either operates against the transport exchange portal system, or the hauler transport management system.
The transport booker can either book a transport with a selected hauler or add a booking request to the transport exchange portal.
Existing transport management system that is integrated with the Instant Mobility systems

The consignee can use a smart phone to later change the drop-off location. The smart phone application will, depending on if the transport was booked with a specific hauler or if the transport booked using the transport exchange portal, interface towards the relevant back-office system.
